  "commonIssues": "<div class=\"accordion\" id=\"issueAccordion\"> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading1\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse1\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Technical Glitches on IGRS</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse1\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>OTP problems and slow systems on the online portal.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Use the <a href=\"https://registration.telangana.gov.in/\" target=\"_blank\">IGRS Telangana</a> portal during non-peak hours. Ensure mobile numbers are Aadhaar-linked.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading2\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse2\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Incorrect Survey Numbers & Dharani</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Rejections due to misalignment between the Will and Dharani/Revenue records.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Cross-verify all land details with Dharani records before drafting.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading3\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse3\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Mutation Delays After Demise</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Transfer of title taking long times at Municipal/Tahsildar offices.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Apply promptly via the Dharani portal or local municipal office with the registered Will, Death Certificate, and Family Member Certificate.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading4\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse4\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Long-Term Legal Challenges</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Wills are often contested leading to property disputes.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Ensure the execution is flawless: attach a medical certificate, register it formally, and perhaps video-record the event.</li></ul></div></div></div> <div class=\"card mb-2\"><div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading5\"><h5 class=\"mb-0\"><button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#collapse5\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\"><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Sub-Registrar Rejections</button></h5></div> <div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"collapse\"><div class=\"card-body\"><p>Authorities refusing registration despite proper documentation.</p><p><strong>How to fix:</strong></p><ul><li>Demand the refusal order in writing. You can appeal to the District Registrar.</li></ul></div></div></div></div>"
